Move 5 units of raw material from (5,5) (location id 2) to (6,6) (target location id 1). This incurs a cost of 5Ã—12+12â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯â¯âˆš=52â¯â¯âˆš
