 and ğ·ğ‘–,ğ‘—
 for 1â‰¤ğ‘–â‰¤ğ‘›
 and 1â‰¤ğ‘—â‰¤ğ‘š
. Also indicate if we are going to maximize or minimize it.

YOUR ANSWER HERE

Next for each source location ğ‘–
, the total amount of material transported from ğ‘–
